Package: ggest
Type: Package
Title: ggplot2 utilities for the Estonian brand platform
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Tanel Pärnamaa
Maintainer: Tanel Pärnamaa <ggest+tanel.parnamaa@gmail.com>
Description: Reusable functions to work with the Estonian brand platform in ggplot2.
    Provides a theme and colour palettes in the Brand Estonia inspired style, and
    plotting functions to visualize data with boulderplots.
